  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Which expression is equivalent to&nbsp;<math alttext=\"15 w squared plus 8 w\"><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow><mi>w</mi></math>?</p>",
